Note that TechnoBBS is still an unfinished product and its being available
to the public for distribution/evaluation/registration is a direct result
of people seeming to be seriously interested in it.  The version numbers
still remain less than 1.  Not because the author is incapable of
increasing the version number by more than 0.01 at a time, but because some
of the features that have been specifically intended for implementation by
the release of version 1.0 are still unfinished.


